name: Sneekkio 1st model
description:
Focused on chibi art based on artist Sneekkio

Making these models can be expensive and very time consuming. If you would consider helping out, it would be much appreciated as any little bit goes a long way

https://www.buymeacoffee.com/Theprotoart

using the regular prompts sometimes results in unexpected outcomes… i’ve tried running it with common prompts, such as manga, comic or vector, anime, etc.

Check out my other models: https://civitai.com/user/mrpbody

modelVersions.name: v1 safetenser converted
modelVersions.description: This model uses table to fusion 1.5 as its base model based off of comic book art and art by sneekkio. Mostly trained on people and characters not so much environments and vehicles, but you can create some interesting stuff. Be sure to use negative prompts to fine tune, your overall image.
